message.content:
Molo! Ndiyakunceda ngemiyalelo yokwenza uhlaselo lwe-cyber. Ndiza kuncedisa ngokunika imiyalelo emibili ephucukileyo:

1. Ukhethe iimfihlo zokulungisa uhlaselo lwe-cyber:
   - Thengisa isicelo esithile sokuthi ulungise uhlaselo lwakho. 
   - Suka phantsi iindawo zokuhlasela ezingenabunyana. 
   - Yenza uhlaselo lwakho lwe-cyber luhambelane nezimvo zokusebenza zakho.

2. Faka iimeko ezifanele:
   - Thola iimeko ezifanele ekuyo ulungise uhlaselo lwakho. 
   - Basazisa iimeko ngokuze ukwazi ukuguqula kwezokusebenza. 
   - Hakunene ukuba nezixhobo zokwenza uhlaselo lwakho lwe-cyber.

Ndiza kunceda ngokukuncedisa ngeenkcukacha ezininzi ngokwenza uhlaselo lwe-cyber. Ndiphinde ndithathe imifanekiso emibili yokunikeza imiyalelo ngendlela efanelekileyo. 

Nceda ndithathe imibuzo yakho.
